al patent attorney.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Such an attorney can leverage their experience to effectively assess your idea and evaluate its potential for obtaining a patent.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">They assist you in navigating the patent application process, addressing any issues that may arise, and avoiding the pitfalls of rejection.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Disclosure\"><\/span><b>Disclosure<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is time to disclose app features and secure court approval for your patent.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The app idea must meet specific requirements, including realism, feasibility, and other eligibility criteria.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You must demonstrate that your idea has the potential to solve a real-world problem or improve existing solutions, while also ensuring that it is practical and achievable.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Patent_Search\"><\/span><b>Patent Search<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To expedite the patent approval process, it is essential for a skilled patent attorney to conduct in-depth patent research.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This analysis enables investigating the patent landscape, potential issues can be identified and addressed proactively, resulting in a smoother and quicker approval process.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Application_Filing\"><\/span><b>Application Filing<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Undoubtedly, the decision to file an application for a patent can be pivotal for the future success of an app.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This decision may be based on factors such as the market size and the uniqueness of the app idea.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A patent filing can either be a provisional or non-provisional patent application, each offering its own benefits and requirements.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Submission\"><\/span><b>Submission<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After completing all the other steps correctly, apply for a patent. Just to draw your attention; this process is lengthy and involves lots of paperwork.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_Much_Does_It_Cost_to_Patent_an_Idea\"><\/span>How Much Does It Cost to Patent an Idea?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-11975 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/How-Much-does-it-Cost-to-Patent-an-Idea.webp\" alt=\"Cost of app patent\" width=\"908\" height=\"441\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/How-Much-does-it-Cost-to-Patent-an-Idea.webp 908w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/How-Much-does-it-Cost-to-Patent-an-Idea-300x146.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/How-Much-does-it-Cost-to-Patent-an-Idea-768x373.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/How-Much-does-it-Cost-to-Patent-an-Idea-150x73.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 908px) 100vw, 908px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The cost of provisional patents ranges from $2,500 to $5,000, hence, it is important for entrepreneurs to carefully evaluate the benefits of securing one.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">On the other hand, when considering all the legal channels involved, the total expenses can increase to a staggering $12,000 to $15,000 per patent.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Elementary filing fee: $70-280+<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Patent search fee: $150-600<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Patent Examination fee: $180-700<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">3.5-year maintenance fee: $400-1600<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">7.5-year maintenance fee: $900-3600<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">11.5-year maintenance fee: $1850-7000+<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>For Detailed fee structure visit the official site of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.uspto.gov\/learning-and-resources\/fees-and-payment\/uspto-fee-schedule#Patent%20Maintenance%20Fee\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">United States Patent and Trademark Office<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_Much_Time_Does_It_Take_to_Patent_Mobile_App_Ideas\"><\/span>How Much Time Does It Take to Patent Mobile App Ideas?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After cost, the next big thing comes how much time it takes to get a mobile app patented.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You should know that there are fair chances of apps getting rejected and resubmitted due to multiple reasons. This process can consume 4 to 6 years or maybe more, depending on the different scenarios involved.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Are there any alternative options for patenting Mobile app ideas?<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Yes, there are!<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Alternatives_to_Patenting_Mobile_App_Ideas\"><\/span>Alternatives to Patenting Mobile App Ideas<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-11967 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/Alternatives-to-Patenting-Mobile-app-ideas.webp\" alt=\"alternates of patent\" width=\"908\" height=\"441\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/Alternatives-to-Patenting-Mobile-app-ideas.webp 908w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/Alternatives-to-Patenting-Mobile-app-ideas-300x146.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/Alternatives-to-Patenting-Mobile-app-ideas-768x373.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/Alternatives-to-Patenting-Mobile-app-ideas-150x73.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 908px) 100vw, 908px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Since <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">patenting is a time-consuming task, it is better to look for alternatives that are less time-consuming and more cost-effective.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Copyright-<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> This patenting alternative is a better choice for preventing unauthorized replication of an app&#8217;s code and user interface. It is cost-effective but it is only effective when someone attempts to directly duplicate the app, and does not cover concepts or functionality.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Trademark-<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> This type of protection is very important to protect the brand image by safeguarding logos, advertisements, catalogs, titles, and designs. It is a good option to prevent imitation or misrepresentation of the brand, preserving its reputation and building trust.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Non-disclosure Agreement-<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> With a non-disclosure agreement (NDA), you add a legal layer to keep specific mobile app-related information confidential, safeguarding the interests of the parties involved. It helps the app&#8217;s sensitive data and trade secrets, and breaching them can lead to a lawsuit\/penalties.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Non-compete Agreement-<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> This agreement ensures that developers work with a company developing similar mobile apps for a fixed period after quitting their current organization. This clause aims to reduce the risk of losing to competition and stop letting information fall into the hands of their rivals.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"To_Patent_or_Not_to_Patent-_Secret_Tips\"><\/span>To Patent or Not to Patent- Secret Tips!<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Well, it is not wrong to say we are living in a competitive world and gradually shifting to a hyperconnected world.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here, apps will connect the communication thread across the globe. Hence, it is not a smart move to overlook m<\/span>obile app ideas<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A unique and valuable idea has the potential to redefine the industry; however, if left unprotected, it can just as easily be consumed by competitors without any guilt.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, the whole process of patenting is a tedious process and is not an ideal choice for an MVP.&nbsp; We at Gozoom Technologies recommend opting for alternatives to patenting if faster time-to-market is your objective and save your resources from getting blocked.<\/span><\/p>\n<div class=\"hbblog-cta\" style=\"background: #fdfdfd!important; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 35px 25px 35px 25px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #dfdfdf; border-radius: 5px; border-bottom-color: #f5bd00; border-bottom-width: 3px!important;\">\n<div class=\"hbblog-cta\">\n<h6 style=\"font-weight: 600; font-size: 24px!important; color: #212121; font-family: 'Open Sans',sans-serif; line-height: 36px;\">Ready to take your mobile app to the next level?<\/h6>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"hbblog-cta-btn\" style=\"margin-top: 20px!important;\"><a style=\"background: #282f6f; color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 3px;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/inquiry.html\">Contact Us<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Final_Verdict\"><\/span><b>Final Verdict<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Indeed, patents can be a tad complex, so it is best to protect your app idea with a reputable and skilled mobile app development company.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you are a forward-thinking company with a unique app idea, then you must connect with the right team of <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/mobile-app-development.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mobile app development company<\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to increase your chances of success.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And this is where Gozoom Technologies is your best bet.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With Gozoom Technologies, you can get a smooth process rollout for app patenting or securing your mobile app idea.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Connect with <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Gozoom Technologies<\/a>&#8211; we ensure that with each app, innovation prevails and opportunities for growth remain unhindered.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_47_1 ez-toc-wrap-left counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-transparent ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/how-to-patent-mobile-app-ideas.html\/#App_Patent-_Is_It_Really_a_Thing\" title=\"App Patent- Is It Really a Thing?\">App Patent- Is It Really a Thing?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a