ing-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-23\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/how-to-patent-mobile-app-ideas.html\/#How_Much_Time_Does_It_Take_to_Patent_Mobile_App_Ideas\" title=\"How Much Time Does It Take to Patent Mobile App Ideas?\">How Much Time Does It Take to Patent Mobile App Ideas?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-24\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/how-to-patent-mobile-app-ideas.html\/#Alternatives_to_Patenting_Mobile_App_Ideas\" title=\"Alternatives to Patenting Mobile App Ideas\">Alternatives to Patenting Mobile App Ideas<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-25\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/how-to-patent-mobile-app-ideas.html\/#To_Patent_or_Not_to_Patent-_Secret_Tips\" title=\"To Patent or Not to Patent- Secret Tips!\">To Patent or Not to Patent- Secret Tips!<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-26\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/how-to-patent-mobile-app-ideas.html\/#Final_Verdict\" title=\"Final Verdict\">Final Verdict<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>A comprehensive guide on how to obtain a patent for your mobile application idea. Learn more about important aspects such as the patenting process, requirements, and strategies for protecting your intellectual property.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":11986,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"ngg_post_thumbnail":0},"categories":[1517],"tags":[2191,2192,2190,2189],"acf":{"show_blog_end":"no","add_blog_end":"","display_hellobar":false,"add_hellobar":"","add_hellobar_link":"","bottom_cta_text":"","bottom_cta_link":"","featured_posts":["no"],"add_text":"","text_color":"#000000","top_cta_text":"","top_cta_link":""},"yoast_head":"